==Description==

The [[Image:Draft_AddToLayer.svg|24px]] '''Draft AddToLayer''' command adds the selected objects to a Layer, or removes them from any layer. {{Version|1.1}}

==Usage==

# Select one or more objects.
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Draft_AddToLayer.svg|16px]] [[Draft_AddToLayer|Add to layer...]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Utilities → [[Image:Draft_AddToLayer.svg|16px]] Add to layer...}} option from the menu.
# If it does not exist the LayerContainer group is created first.
# A new layer is added to the LayerContainer group.


